This place felt like a paradise tucked away in Phuket 🌴☀️
Stayed at @barcelo_coconut_island and I couldn’t get enough — beautiful villas, two stunning pool areas, their own island, and a 24/7 boat service that makes exploring super smooth.
The property is huge, the aesthetics are perfect for content creators, and the food? Absolutely amazing. 🍽️✨
Plus, the hospitality was on point — such a wholesome and peaceful escape.
Highly recommend this gem if you’re heading to Phuket!
